<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .note {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #007BFF;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffeeba;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Termux & Termux-API</h1>

    <div class="warning">
        <h3>⚠️ It is recommended to install both Termux and Termux-API from the same source.</h3>
    </div>

    <h2>🌐 From GitHub:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/termux/termux-app/releases/latest" target="_blank">Termux</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/termux/termux-api/releases/latest" target="_blank">Termux API</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>🌐 From F-Droid:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://f-droid.org/packages/com.termux.api" target="_blank">Termux APK</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://f-droid.org/packages/com.termux" target="_blank">Termux API APK</a></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="note">
        <h3>💡 Note: If you are facing issues recognizing your device through ADB & Fastboot commands, consider using termux-monet:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/Termux-Monet/termux-monet/releases" target="_blank">Termux Monet</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/Termux-Monet/termux-api/releases" target="_blank">Termux API Monet</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

</body>
</html>